{"title":"Parser skeleton: guided diff tour","gitnotes":1,"type":"markdown","body":"## Start here\n\nThis commit wires tokenizer → parser but **does not** parse body text yet.\n\n### Tour\n\n1. Open [parseEnvelope entry](gitnotes:diff/examples/demo/parser/src/parser.ts#R4-R12) — validates `{` then title-first rule.\n2. Then [version gate](gitnotes:diff/examples/demo/parser/src/parser.ts#R18-R21) — rejects unknown `gitnotes` values.\n3. Skim [skipTo helper](gitnotes:diff/examples/demo/parser/src/parser.ts#R34-R41) — linear scan, not a real JSON parser.\n\n### Checklist\n\n- [x] Returns `ParseResult` on all paths\n- [x] `ParseOptions` stub added to types\n- [ ] Full string extraction for title/body (commit 09)\n\n> **Reviewer note:** placeholder envelope on success is intentional scaffolding — do not treat as production-ready parsing."}
